  <graph edgedefault="directed" id="G">
    <data key="d0" xml:space="preserve"><![CDATA[
      State machine for yogi_posting_events.event_type.
      Each node corresponds to a row written to yogi_posting_events.
      "dismissed"  = quick instinctive skip (minimal rationale expected).
      "not_applied" = deliberate decision after research (rationale required for Bewerbungsprotokoll).
      Both "dismissed" and "not_applied" fold into the old "no-go" state.
      "viewed"     absorbs the old "interested" state (clicking for details).
      "saved"      absorbs the old "favorites" state.
      "outcome_received" is new — employer reply to a submitted application.
    ]]></data>
